            "text": "<p>\"I love Mokosh brand products , it absorbs quickly, for the day I use together with the cream, for the night only oil alone. <br/>I feel that the skin is very well moisturized and is not greasy. I recommend.\"</p>",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 80,
